data.description: VIEW Lake Tahuya, pristine turn key ONE LEVEL 3bd/2bath view home on almost 1/2 acre! Terraced & parklike w/beautiful trees & rhoddies. Plenty of parking & RV space w/water hook up. Extremely well maintained w/fantastic open floor plan. Features vaulted & high ceilings throughout. Open concept lives large & airy w/well equipped kitchen, abundant cabinetry & central island flowing seamlessly to dining, family & living rm.  Primary w/ensuite & large WIC. 2 additional bedrms share full bath. Home in like new condition, a must see. Private Lake w/community park/beach/boat launch where you can picnic, swim, fish & watersports. State ORV trails! Shipyard Bangor PSNS all less than 30 min drive! Seller offering 10K towards Buyers closing costs.
